title: Xenogears -- Creid
description:
"Creid (Gaelic for "Believe") is a Celtic-style CD, with a multitude of instruments. There are vocal and instrumental songs including the Japanese versions of "Star of Tears" (track 2) and "Small of Two Pieces" (track 10). Maire Breatnach, known for her work in Final Fantasy IV: Celtic Moon, also contributed a great deal on this CD."
